The one constant… FAMILY 💙 
Started and ended the year with these special souls. 
In between; memories and priceless moments! RV camping, Gualala Point, Oahu, Carlsbad, San Diego, hikes, runs, games, cuddles, movies… laughter and love!! 
A reminder that life works out exactly as it should 🙌🏼 #niecesandnephew #littlebrother #family #travel #makingmemories

This is me! #Awakening 
Showing up just as I am- not perfect, not always ‘pretty’, not curated… just joyful to be alive and breathing in beach air. 

“Courage starts with showing up and letting ourselves be seen.” ~ Brene Brown 

For 10 years on this platform- every post, every word, every image… analyzed, curated and perfected. It’s EXHAUSTING and really ruins your peace! I have no desire to play that game anymore. After a deep and honest conversation with my nieces about social media and self esteem I realized that being held captive was no longer serving me and setting a really bad example for them. So… moving forward- I post what I want-when I want! Some shots will be rad, some will be meaningful, some will seem irrelevant … but they will all be MINE!! ⚡️⚡️

Focus! ⚡️ As the saying goes “your focus determines your reality”! I love the battle ropes because they take both strength and rhythm. You’ve gotta be in the flow. Kinda like life I guess. 

Truly grateful for my friendship with @tinamuir88 💜💙… she recently reminded me that what I thought I was focusing on was really just a distraction from what I NEEDED to be paying attention to. How often do we focus on the big thing or the ‘easy’ thing and ignore the important and hard things? #friendship #choices #bigdecisions #workout #sunshine
